  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Soak cedar planks in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Thread chicken, onion, carrot, celery, and garlic onto skewers.",
    "Brush skewers with olive oil and season with salt, black pepper, and almond extract.",
    "Place skewers on cedar planks and grill for 15 minutes per side.",
    "Let skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with parsley and serve immediately.",
    "Discard cedar planks after use."
